{"build_type":"library","description":"As-completed compile ASSESSOR (producer). Receives nothing but the collector channel; it CREATES the work. Self-contained: it knows where the source is and what to do. Lists the source package dir, builds the shared schema (all struct_definitions + module_globals) in pass 1, then in pass 2 pushes one SELF-CONTAINED work item JSON per package {schema + that package's function + objdir} to the channel and closes. No globals, no inputs, no files -- the JSON bridge carries everything to the per-function compile workers.","module_name":"produce-compile-worklist-feeding-collector","package_name":"produce-compile-worklist-feeding-collector","function_definitions":{"produce-compile-worklist-feeding-collector":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"channel","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"zero","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"i_j","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"i_n","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":1},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"i_names","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":2},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"i_root","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":3},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"i_ch","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":4},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"i_ms","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":5},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"i_mg","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":6},{"